\[\displaystyle{\pi_1 \left\{\begin{array}{ll}x = -1 + 2\lambda +3\mu \\y = 4\lambda - \mu \\z = 2 - 3\lambda + 2\mu\end{array}\right.} \hspace{0.5cm} \quad\text{y} \hspace{1cm} \displaystyle{\pi_2 \left\{2x-5y+z=0 \right.}\]
